:1473682,"uid":27198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e8ba6e6c3a6f685078954b533e6cdd0d7c7d9d","tid":1473682,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共見到就自然對放自由行落黎有所顧慮，將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cbc09p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cbc09p.png&h=55d383ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲打可以用下面條link去印文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/3/folders/1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F3%2Ffolders%2F1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=3604ff7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/3/folders/1x95q3KBq0_0HBlGnIRXLw8qzQEwxs-Rg</a>"},{"pid":"df0492734527d2a577ea80177d8033e2a4906f8c","tid":1473682,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"燒佢後爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c6b87fb646fc72884fec269a7d1310f76cf3f1","tid":1473682,"uid":199613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"輸出革命唔係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係要同佢地分享經驗教佢地點搞革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2916ab